T1  - A Two-Moment Approximation for the Mean Waiting Time in the GI/G/s Queue
AU  - Kimura, Toshikazu
Y1  - 1986/06/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.32.6.751
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.32.6.751
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 751
EP  - 763
VL  - 32
IS  - 6
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - We provide a simple two-moment approximation formula for the mean waiting time in a GI/G/s queue. This formula has the form of a certain combination of the exact mean waiting times for the D/M/s, M/D/s and M/M/s queues, and hence it can be easily calculated by using some queueing tables. The quality of the approximation is tested by comparing it with known solutions in particular cases.
AB  - We provide a simple two-moment approximation formula for the mean waiting time in a GI/G/s queue. This formula has the form of a certain combination of the exact mean waiting times for the D/M/s, M/D/s and M/M/s queues, and hence it can be easily calculated by using some queueing tables. The quality of the approximation is tested by comparing it with known solutions in particular cases.
